text.tspan: Final version of the coded signal: introduced July 1994
ID OR MI OE P1 ME GM GS P2
P1 = odd parity bit for the first information group
GS = day of the week (1 = monday, ..., 7 = sunday)
P2 = odd parity bit for the second information group
SE = notice of DST time change
PA = second frame odd parity bit
1 1 1 no change in the next 7 days
00 no leap second within the month
10 1 leap second delay at the end of the month
11 1 leap second early at the end of the month
